  <summary date="2021-09-02T14:07:47Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protect Women's and Girls' Rights in Afghanistan Act of 2021

This bill requires the Department of State to periodically report to Congress on the conditions of women and girls in Afghan civil society following the departure of U.S. and NATO forces. The reports shall also assess the status of assurances made by the Taliban related to preserving the rights of women and girls in Afghanistan.</summary>
